QCg&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c0ef4a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a_2rxHlkQCg</a><br />\n<br />\n主題曲－長坡橋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/videos/10155979514607230/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FundergroundDV%2Fvideos%2F10155979514607230%2F&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=de57b4af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/videos/10155979514607230/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/142554_07f139fa103e3a2adf1d1c3e536a1639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F142554_07f139fa103e3a2adf1d1c3e536a1639.jpg&h=c059564e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc61df3a87912d334faff0fdbf751918cd30033f","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"比賽一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/photos/a.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229/10156001336127230/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FundergroundDV%2Fphotos%2Fa.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229%2F10156001336127230%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2a8f442c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/photos/a.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229/10156001336127230/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n為了感謝玩家熱烈支持，將送出價值$8980 名貴SONY 49 吋LCD 電視！<br />\n活動名稱： Speed Run 極速擊殺「困難難度」董卓 ! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽二<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/photos/a.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229/10156009800807230/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FundergroundDV%2Fphotos%2Fa.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229%2F10156009800807230%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=019737f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergroundDV/photos/a.10150904765627230.445032.218359782229/10156009800807230/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n活動名稱： 連擊王選拔大賽<br />\n參加方法：上載閣下連擊數最高的影片（上載到youtube再複製連結回覆"},{"pid":"be659e9ee6d06b5c9674e99fda83ef332aedf670","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"新手忠告:&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n1.先玩普通模式<br />\n<br />\n2. 必升角色(3隻):&nbsp;<br />\n小木(40lv會覺醒, 但同時要上到60lv先有援助技, 自行考慮hold唔hold住39lv為左援助技)<br />\n鳳雛(全game唯一補血, 必用, 必練)<br />\n關羽(超早有得用, 低魂買, 攻高)<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好玩盾角, 血相對其他角色唔係多好多, 攻就少60%<br />\n<br />\n4. 卡關就努力刷關升lv, 升完又簡單ko&nbsp;<br />\n(除左某d boss要注意攻擊時機, 唔一定要連combo, e.g. 夏侯惇一開防反技, 你就唔好打佢, 一打中佢, 佢就hyper mode玩全畫面攻擊n秒, 實死無生) <br />\n<br />\nby黃小鳥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：普通同困難有咩分別？<br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：只有血量差別，玩家血量係困難會低啲。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：邊關刷錢最快？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :&nbsp;6-7"},{"pid":"767718c06947ce5c9d9370df75da3e9e9b3cd95d","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"99LV後角色數據by maymood<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/081337_f47454d1d3644127f42070181a8b9afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F081337_f47454d1d3644127f42070181a8b9afc.jpg&h=ca21eee6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3f5fcecd774be84e80eddcc7b810fba0555c2a4","tid":556141,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"上面張圖唔係我po..<br />\n<br />\n若以方便各位參考為目的, 咁我只係po過幾張資料整合<br />\n<br />\n血攻圖(普通難度), 困難難度只影響hp值, 即hp*2/3, or *0.6667<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/173551_803c2219d1750da94f9c15da7e352414.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F173551_803c2219d1750da94f9c15da7e352414.png&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4e6ff46d\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/173551_803c2219d1750da94f9c15da7e352414.png</a><br />\n<br />\n刷錢圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/173731_d5c7796f0d1b287626a2fa17dc6fa04f.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F173731_d5c7796f0d1b287626a2fa17dc6fa04f.png&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1ed6aec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/173731_d5c7796f0d1b287626a2fa17dc6fa04f.png</a><br />\n<br />\n窮人/新手刷錢組合<br />\n99張角+99劉備+99張飛 (升lv所需$好少, 抵升), 角2&gt;飛3&gt;劉3&gt;角3, 4秒1場<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/174147_48e2853617b4144ac7a3772dd450e3b7.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F174147_48e2853617b4144ac7a3772dd450e3b7.jpg&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=acf24615\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/174147_48e2853617b4144ac7a3772dd450e3b7.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n技傷圖, 英雄同lv情況下實際輸出<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/174332_5d2b15fe9efc648e7838091f207940d1.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F174332_5d2b15fe9efc648e7838091f207940d1.png&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6b0b60d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/174332_5d2b15fe9efc648e7838091f207940d1.png</a>"},{"pid":"85b292b6e4ed2e4cada3d4042d75e89734394712","tid":556141,"uid":165126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"推到達哥送電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef0f1ef9208a678bf8e092ceb65e2ca5fe30797","tid":556141,"uid":164245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"到此一遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2685bf2fb41dcf6b312a30ce84bad1a2f0805761","tid":556141,"uid":164247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:21:11.000Z","msg":"竟然開到2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f8b6e7993b2bc78eb5ea65dd93cc07911d5eab","tid":556141,"uid":166623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1348c5a4f2e19b1fc83b66b753a0fdd33b1ad9d0","tid":556141,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7f8b6e7993b2bc78eb5ea65dd93cc07911d5eab","tid":556141,"uid":166623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"連擊會強化傷害, 40之後乜野廢招都秒殺d敵人咁濟, 連到仲要好講運氣<br />\n除左「試煉」, 其他關(任何英雄組合/遊戲難度)最高連擊可能性唔會多過70"},{"pid":"f63c80d7d198618fe35d341aec0f496ac3ba11f6","tid":556141,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"補充下,<br />\n<br />\n* 「夏侯」關卡防反, 就算正面硬食亦唔算好痛<br />\n　 另外用無敵技打佢係會照扣佢血, 可打快d<br />\n* 鳳搓係唯1補師, 唔理佢1技有冇打中人, <br />\n　 成功出晒就會全員4人回復<span style=\"color: red;\">45%</span>血<br />\n* 小木40lv以後, 每升1lv所需$係與同lv呂布同級, <br />\n　係所有英雄中最貴, 即係成本最貴, 其次係夏侯<br />\n* 大型盾怪會中斷你某d技/唔受某d技影響, 先破佢霸體較佳<br />\n* 劉備1技除左破霸體, 攻擊範圍限定中場右場(非常穩定)<br />\n　 劉備2技非無敵技, 但效果比無敵技更屈, 會定怪<br />\n　 定怪期間可放其他英雄援助技做d你想順利出到既技, ie.補血<br />\n* 會將怪推左既技: 木3, 劉1, 鳳1<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(last hit必須擊中)</span>, 關1<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(怪必須在中或右場)</span>, 慈1<br />\n* 會將怪推右既技: 木1, 覺2, 鳳2, 飛1, 周1, 呂2, 呂3"},{"pid":"6f05a415293531ba2df0e03c5811a95bac25455c","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63c80d7d198618fe35d341aec0f496ac3ba11f6","tid":556141,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"補充下,<br />\n<br />\n* 「夏侯」關卡防反, 就算正面硬食亦唔算好痛<br />\n　 另外用無敵技打佢係會照扣佢血, 可打快d<br />\n* 鳳搓係唯1補師, 唔理佢1技有冇打中人, <br />\n　 成功出晒就會全員4人回復<span style=\"color: red;\">45%</span>血<br />\n* 小木40lv以後, 每升1lv所需$係與同lv呂布同級, <br />\n　係所有英雄中最貴, 即係成本最貴, 其次係夏侯<br />\n* 大型盾怪會中斷你某d技/唔受某d技影響, 先破佢霸體較佳<br />\n* 劉備1技除左破霸體, 攻擊範圍限定中場右場(非常穩定)<br />\n　 劉備2技非無敵技, 但效果比無敵技更屈, 會定怪<br />\n　 定怪期間可放其他英雄援助技做d你想順利出到既技, ie.補血<br />\n* 會將怪推左既技: 木3, 劉1, 鳳1<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(last hit必須擊中)</span>, 關1<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(怪必須在中或右場)</span>, 慈1<br />\n* 會將怪推右既技: 木1, 覺2, 鳳2, 飛1, 周1, 呂2, 呂3"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"劉備2技其實幾好用，係衰在佢出完會擺POSE係度俾人打個下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80171efd40105e81691c67e6423605a7226c3b85","tid":556141,"uid":165126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"擺POSE之後比人噴火死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8257ed966cfe0c5ed96ba284e7d7795ec1823e88","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80171efd40105e81691c67e6423605a7226c3b85","tid":556141,"uid":165126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"擺POSE之後比人噴火死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"果種7真係幾似達哥"},{"pid":"ada5010858e639caac39bfbbbb091a927d34e2a5","tid":556141,"uid":164247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8257ed966cfe0c5ed96ba284e7d7795ec1823e88","tid":556141,"uid":39670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80171efd40105e81691c67e6423605a7226c3b85","tid":556141,"uid":165126,"like"